                        <Label alignment="TOP_LEFT" prefHeight="210.0" prefWidth="638.0" styleClass="text" stylesheets="@../css/help.css" text="You can begin your journey to better planned learning by creating your Mirus &#10;planner account.&#10;&#10;With its straightforward design, this planner software allows you to create a &#10;TO-DO list and provides insight into your tasks and subjects.&#10;You receive tokens as you complete activities on your TO-DO list, which you can &#10;use to play an in-app game during study breaks. &#10;This planner software is aimed towards students and learners who find it &#10;difficult to maintain their commitments to their academic and extracurricular &#10;activities. &#10;" BorderPane.alignment="CENTER">
